data.description:
Welcome to this 4 Bedroom 2 Bath oasis with 2 Living Areas (downstairs game room could be 5th Bedroom). The
heart of this home is the stunning kitchen with granite countertops and tons of counter and cabinet space. Whether you're an aspiring chef or a casual cook, you'll appreciate this large kitchen that opens to the breakfast nook and living area. The two spacious living areas are perfect for both formal gatherings and cozy movie nights. The versatility of these spaces allows you to customize your living experience. The freshly painted interiors in neutral tones throughout to provide a blank canvas for your personal decor and design ideas. Enjoy the serenity of nature with the mature trees. These natural beauties provide shade and tranquility, making it an ideal spot for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. A brand-new fence encloses your private haven. Detached shed could be used for storage or a fun indoor/outdoor living space. Close to the updated New Orleans Square area with an abundance of shopping and dining, Easy access to the Creek Turnpike.
